sentences: Susanne Abbuehl (born July 30, 1970) is a Swiss/Dutch jazz singer and composer.
In 2001, her album April was released by ECM  and won an Edison award (Dutch Grammy).

In May 2006, her album Compass was released by ECM (with Michel Portal).
In 2013, her radio play Der Gaukler Tag was nominated for the Prix Marulic.
